1
00:00:14,575 --> 00:00:20,013
<i>Connecting old words</i>
<i>that have been used up</i>

2
00:00:20,847 --> 00:00:28,754
<i>I just want to convey</i>
<i>my simple thoughts</i>

3
00:00:28,822 --> 00:00:34,192
<i>That day's faint wind blows away</i>

4
00:00:34,261 --> 00:00:38,322
<i>at the castle ruins of yesterday</i>

5
00:00:39,566 --> 00:00:44,469
<i>I'll laugh with you</i>
<i>and live for the moment</i>

6
00:00:45,205 --> 00:00:52,111
<i>Still that incident</i>
<i>will continue to trouble you, right?</i>

7
00:00:53,513 --> 00:00:57,005
<i>That's why it must be good bye</i>

8
00:00:57,084 --> 00:01:04,047
<i>Leaving nothing behind,</i>
<i>let us share what is left</i>

9
00:01:04,124 --> 00:01:11,189
<i>In time, we'll realize</i>
<i>that it was everything</i>

10
00:01:11,264 --> 00:01:17,931
<i>And sadness will touch our cheeks,</i>
<i>creating a river of tears</i>

11
00:01:18,405 --> 00:01:27,905
<i>Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex</i>
<i>and melting away</i>

12
00:01:40,804 --> 00:01:44,365
Not yet? Idate hasn't come, yet?

13
00:01:48,579 --> 00:01:50,945
My lord, we finally found evidence

14
00:01:51,014 --> 00:01:53,175
regarding the matter
we were investigating.

15
00:01:53,884 --> 00:01:55,715
Oh, I see.

16
00:01:58,388 --> 00:02:00,322
Mm, good work.

17
00:02:02,225 --> 00:02:04,090
My lord, is there something amiss?

18
00:02:04,294 --> 00:02:06,455
No, it's nothing

19
00:02:10,300 --> 00:02:12,291
<i>Concentrate on my Chakra.</i>

20
00:02:45,102 --> 00:02:46,330
We're saved.

21
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:51,631
Sasuke, are you okay?

22
00:02:58,949 --> 00:03:00,576
Naruto, I'm counting on you.

23
00:03:01,451 --> 00:03:02,679
Protect Idate.

24
00:03:03,253 --> 00:03:08,350
<i>The Last Leg.</i>
<i>A Final Act of Desperation</i>

25
00:03:12,396 --> 00:03:15,229
Poison needles won't work on me.

26
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:20,192
How dare you do that
to Sasuke and Sakura?!

27
00:03:20,470 --> 00:03:21,630
Rest easy.

28
00:03:22,205 --> 00:03:25,641
I'll send you to the place
where they are real soon.

29
00:03:26,643 --> 00:03:28,736
I won't go so easily!

30
00:03:33,917 --> 00:03:34,576
<i>Naruto.</i>

31
00:03:35,752 --> 00:03:37,583
<i>But what do I do?</i>

32
00:03:38,155 --> 00:03:40,715
<i>The Rasengan</i>
<i>won't work on his sword.</i>

33
00:03:42,626 --> 00:03:43,684
It doesn't matter.

34
00:03:44,161 --> 00:03:46,288
Those two are waiting for my help!

35
00:03:47,631 --> 00:03:49,189
Saving each other again, huh?!

36
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:52,762
They wouldn't survive
falling off this cliff.

37
00:03:53,036 --> 00:03:53,968
Shut up!

38
00:03:54,271 --> 00:03:56,205
Multi Shadow Clone Jutsu.

39
00:04:04,815 --> 00:04:09,411
Oh... you're going to run away
from here using such a diversion?

40
00:04:09,820 --> 00:04:12,653
Don't mess with me!
Who's going to run away?

41
00:04:33,710 --> 00:04:37,237
Naruto, it's futile.
That technique won't work on that sword!

42
00:04:38,181 --> 00:04:38,909
It's futile!

43
00:04:49,426 --> 00:04:50,222
Naruto!

44
00:04:52,028 --> 00:04:54,553
Just like the Uchiha loser earlier,

45
00:04:54,831 --> 00:04:58,130
why is it that each and every
Leaf Village Ninja is an idiot?

46
00:04:59,569 --> 00:05:00,558
Shut up!

47
00:05:01,338 --> 00:05:03,169
I'm going to save those two!

48
00:05:03,373 --> 00:05:06,240
Are you seriously thinking
they're alive after falling off this cliff?

49
00:05:06,977 --> 00:05:09,138
You should've gotten out of here.

50
00:05:10,914 --> 00:05:11,938
As if...

51
00:05:14,584 --> 00:05:18,384
I'd abandon my comrades
and run away!

52
00:05:19,422 --> 00:05:22,687
That's my answer to the tenth problem!

53
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:25,625
What're you saying?

54
00:05:26,530 --> 00:05:27,292
One more time.

55
00:05:30,333 --> 00:05:31,493
Eat this.

56
00:05:33,136 --> 00:05:34,000
Idiot.

57
00:05:34,604 --> 00:05:35,764
Rasengan!

58
00:05:45,816 --> 00:05:47,010
Naruto!

59
00:05:54,991 --> 00:05:58,825
You still don't get it?!
You don't have a chance of winning!

60
00:06:00,564 --> 00:06:01,963
Damn!

61
00:06:13,176 --> 00:06:13,972
<i>That's...</i>

62
00:06:17,914 --> 00:06:20,815
<i>the damage Sasuke inflicted.</i>

63
00:06:22,385 --> 00:06:23,249
<i>That's it!</i>

64
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,512
<i>If I aim for that...</i>

65
00:06:27,691 --> 00:06:28,350
<i>I can win!</i>

66
00:06:28,658 --> 00:06:32,219
You saying you still want to fight?
Give it up, already!

67
00:06:32,662 --> 00:06:35,096
Shut up! Shadow Clone Jutsu!

68
00:06:38,435 --> 00:06:39,265
Sasuke...

69
00:06:39,769 --> 00:06:43,034
Sasuke gave me a chance!
I won't waste it!

70
00:06:44,841 --> 00:06:45,569
Naruto...

71
00:06:50,714 --> 00:06:51,874
<i>Stay still!</i>

72
00:06:54,684 --> 00:06:57,175
<i>Sasuke! They're using</i>
<i>the Water Clone Jutsu!</i>

73
00:06:58,154 --> 00:06:58,916
<i>I know!</i>

74
00:07:01,625 --> 00:07:04,389
<i>Trust us, Idate!</i>
<i>We'll protect you, no matter what!</i>

75
00:07:07,530 --> 00:07:09,088
<i>S-Sakura...</i>

76
00:07:09,833 --> 00:07:13,599
<i>Go on ahead.</i>
<i>We'll be right behind you.</i>

77
00:07:15,705 --> 00:07:16,399
<i>Sakura!</i>

78
00:07:20,877 --> 00:07:21,809
I...

79
00:07:23,046 --> 00:07:26,914
I hate people who don't know
when to quit.

80
00:07:28,385 --> 00:07:29,852
This is the end.

81
00:07:38,328 --> 00:07:39,886
A foolish cheap trick.

82
00:07:44,567 --> 00:07:45,158
What?!

83
00:07:48,805 --> 00:07:52,002
I'm saying I can't stand this
saving each other business.

84
00:07:52,075 --> 00:07:53,372
Idate!

85
00:07:55,045 --> 00:07:56,808
Your opponent is over here!

86
00:07:59,182 --> 00:08:00,012
Above!

87
00:08:03,420 --> 00:08:04,580
Rasengan!

88
00:08:15,966 --> 00:08:16,591
What?!

89
00:08:23,306 --> 00:08:24,170
It can't be!

90
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:38,180
Naruto, you did it!

91
00:08:42,525 --> 00:08:43,321
Naruto...

92
00:08:44,160 --> 00:08:46,390
You're really something.

93
00:08:49,332 --> 00:08:50,560
Yeah, well...

94
00:08:51,201 --> 00:08:51,860
Sakura!

95
00:08:56,439 --> 00:08:59,272
Naruto! Idate...!

96
00:09:00,310 --> 00:09:01,140
Sakura!

97
00:09:01,811 --> 00:09:02,869
She's okay?

98
00:09:04,381 --> 00:09:06,372
Sasuke's okay, too.

99
00:09:07,183 --> 00:09:09,549
I'm coming to save you now,
believe it.

100
00:09:09,753 --> 00:09:14,122
Idiot. Forget about us and
get going to the finish line, quick!

101
00:09:14,958 --> 00:09:16,448
Oh, that's right.

102
00:09:17,093 --> 00:09:20,028
But what should we do about this?

103
00:09:20,430 --> 00:09:21,556
Leave it to me.

104
00:09:25,301 --> 00:09:28,634
We'll cut the rope and go
to the opposite bank in one swing!

105
00:09:29,672 --> 00:09:30,639
I get it!

106
00:09:34,210 --> 00:09:37,202
I thought the worst of myself.

107
00:09:39,249 --> 00:09:42,241
But Boss Jirocho trusted in me.

108
00:09:43,386 --> 00:09:46,378
<i>I trust you more than anyone.</i>

109
00:09:47,791 --> 00:09:52,194
It was the first time
I was trusted by someone.

110
00:09:53,596 --> 00:09:57,589
So I wanted to win this race
for the boss, no matter what.

111
00:09:58,802 --> 00:10:01,635
But in reality, I can't win
just with such feelings.

112
00:10:02,739 --> 00:10:04,798
So many times along the way,
I felt like giving up.

113
00:10:05,475 --> 00:10:06,100
<i>Watch out!</i>

114
00:10:06,443 --> 00:10:07,740
But each time,

115
00:10:07,811 --> 00:10:11,770
you guys risked your lives
to save a lame duck like me!

116
00:10:16,419 --> 00:10:17,909
Naruto, I'm sorry.

117
00:10:18,521 --> 00:10:20,751
I should've trusted you guys
from the start.

118
00:10:21,691 --> 00:10:23,181
What're you saying?

119
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:26,593
Say stuff like that
after winning the race.

120
00:10:28,498 --> 00:10:29,396
You're right.

121
00:10:32,469 --> 00:10:33,060
Naruto!

122
00:10:42,445 --> 00:10:43,309
Idate!

123
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:45,747
Okay, do it!

124
00:10:46,149 --> 00:10:46,843
Right!

125
00:11:15,245 --> 00:11:18,840
Boo! Boo! Boo!

126
00:11:20,617 --> 00:11:21,845
Now that's a rousing welcome.

127
00:11:24,420 --> 00:11:27,480
Naruto, at this rate,
we'll crash into the rocks!

128
00:11:27,757 --> 00:11:30,123
I know. Leave it to me!

129
00:11:30,426 --> 00:11:33,190
Release Chakra from
the bottom of my feet.

130
00:11:33,763 --> 00:11:36,561
It's the very last Chakra!

131
00:11:38,835 --> 00:11:40,803
Then stick to
the rocks with Chakra!

132
00:11:47,777 --> 00:11:49,711
All right, Naruto!

133
00:11:50,146 --> 00:11:52,512
Now dash to the finish line!

134
00:11:52,749 --> 00:11:57,652
Sakura, I'll come back
to help you right away!

135
00:11:58,221 --> 00:11:59,848
Okay. Let's go, Idate.

136
00:12:00,089 --> 00:12:00,680
Right!

137
00:12:08,298 --> 00:12:09,822
Run steady, Fukusuke!

138
00:12:10,166 --> 00:12:11,690
Stay sharp until the end.

139
00:12:11,935 --> 00:12:14,768
Shut up! I know.

140
00:12:15,138 --> 00:12:19,336
Geez... spoiling my good mood.

141
00:12:23,279 --> 00:12:26,578
I can see the Todoroki Great Shrine.

142
00:12:30,553 --> 00:12:31,281
Boss!

143
00:12:31,521 --> 00:12:32,488
Blast it!

144
00:12:37,927 --> 00:12:39,053
<i>Good, good.</i>

145
00:12:40,997 --> 00:12:41,929
Idate.

146
00:12:42,599 --> 00:12:43,793
- Hey!
- Oh!

147
00:12:43,866 --> 00:12:45,094
Hey! What's that?

148
00:12:45,868 --> 00:12:46,800
Here he comes!

149
00:12:47,403 --> 00:12:49,428
Idate of the Wasabi Family's here!

150
00:12:54,410 --> 00:12:55,308
Go!

151
00:12:55,612 --> 00:12:56,874
You can still catch up!

152
00:13:02,285 --> 00:13:02,842
What?!

153
00:13:05,521 --> 00:13:06,385
Idate!

154
00:13:09,325 --> 00:13:10,314
Idiot!

155
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:13,390
What're you doing, Fukusuke?! Run!

156
00:13:14,964 --> 00:13:15,988
Damn it!

157
00:13:17,233 --> 00:13:18,200
I won't lose.

158
00:13:19,068 --> 00:13:21,195
I will <i>not</i> lose!

159
00:13:25,975 --> 00:13:29,706
I won't give up until the very end!

160
00:13:33,950 --> 00:13:38,353
Like heck. I won't be passed up
after I've come this far!

161
00:13:40,823 --> 00:13:42,848
- All right!
- He caught up.

162
00:13:46,462 --> 00:13:48,157
<i>Blast this guy...!</i>

163
00:13:48,564 --> 00:13:51,055
I won't lose, you little...!

164
00:13:54,404 --> 00:13:55,132
<i>Blast...</i>

165
00:13:58,808 --> 00:13:59,740
Idate...!

166
00:14:00,777 --> 00:14:02,404
Come on, Idate!

167
00:14:02,879 --> 00:14:03,641
<i>Boss!</i>

168
00:14:10,219 --> 00:14:14,417
Go! Idate...!

169
00:14:15,758 --> 00:14:18,727
All right!

170
00:15:00,002 --> 00:15:01,094
I did it!

171
00:15:11,314 --> 00:15:12,338
Idate.

172
00:15:12,915 --> 00:15:14,382
You ran a fine race.

173
00:15:15,518 --> 00:15:16,143
Boss!

174
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,446
You did well.

175
00:15:19,389 --> 00:15:23,018
Boss, I'm sorry. I'm truly sorry.

176
00:15:23,593 --> 00:15:26,391
You fool. What're you apologizing for?

177
00:15:27,029 --> 00:15:28,360
You won.

178
00:15:28,765 --> 00:15:30,494
No, please let me speak.

179
00:15:31,067 --> 00:15:35,299
I really want to apologize now.
I'm truly sorry!

180
00:15:36,038 --> 00:15:39,701
You're making no sense to me.
What a totally weird guy.

181
00:15:40,209 --> 00:15:41,801
Well done, Idate.

182
00:15:42,078 --> 00:15:43,102
I was wrong about you.

183
00:15:43,746 --> 00:15:47,079
Okay, Idate.
Go receive the winner's blessing.

184
00:15:47,984 --> 00:15:48,473
Yes!

185
00:15:58,961 --> 00:16:00,451
Hey, Idate!

186
00:16:07,770 --> 00:16:09,294
Hey, you idiot!

187
00:16:09,739 --> 00:16:13,835
Bringing shame upon the boss!
You're prepared, aren't you?

188
00:16:14,477 --> 00:16:16,035
I-I'm sorry!

189
00:16:17,380 --> 00:16:18,404
The winner!

190
00:16:18,648 --> 00:16:22,448
Idate Morino of the Wasabi Family!

191
00:16:26,055 --> 00:16:29,252
He finally did it.

192
00:16:30,293 --> 00:16:33,262
Hey, hey... Just a minute.

193
00:16:34,597 --> 00:16:35,461
Kyuroku.

194
00:16:35,932 --> 00:16:39,925
Along the way, he rode
on the back of a hired Ninja.

195
00:16:40,736 --> 00:16:42,033
This is a violation.

196
00:16:42,438 --> 00:16:43,427
W-What?

197
00:16:43,806 --> 00:16:45,068
There's proof.

198
00:16:45,808 --> 00:16:47,639
Look at this photo.

199
00:16:50,880 --> 00:16:55,715
Racing until the end on your own strength
is the rule of this race.

200
00:16:56,385 --> 00:16:58,512
Therefore, Idate is disqualified.

201
00:17:00,623 --> 00:17:04,787
The winner is Fukusuke Hikyakuya
of the Wagarashi Family.

202
00:17:06,128 --> 00:17:06,890
No way.

203
00:17:07,096 --> 00:17:08,723
H-Hold it. That was...!

204
00:17:08,865 --> 00:17:12,961
I'll hear no excuses!
Jirocho, it's a promise.

205
00:17:13,035 --> 00:17:16,630
I order the Wasabi Family
dissolved immediately.

206
00:17:18,040 --> 00:17:19,166
Just a minute.

207
00:17:20,276 --> 00:17:23,370
There is no such rule anywhere.
Do not speak nonsense!

208
00:17:23,846 --> 00:17:25,040
M-My lord!

209
00:17:26,015 --> 00:17:27,346
Or perhaps...

210
00:17:27,517 --> 00:17:31,078
you have a reason for wanting
the Wagarashi to win at all cost?

211
00:17:31,487 --> 00:17:32,977
No, nothing like that.

212
00:17:33,856 --> 00:17:38,452
Could it be because you would
not be able to do things like this?

213
00:17:39,629 --> 00:17:40,459
Look.

214
00:17:42,498 --> 00:17:46,628
You fool!
Retire and enter the monastery!

215
00:17:47,036 --> 00:17:48,970
Yes, yes, my lord!

216
00:17:49,372 --> 00:17:50,839
Kyuroku Wagarashi.

217
00:17:50,907 --> 00:17:52,101
Y-Yes?

218
00:17:52,542 --> 00:17:55,375
Word of your evil deeds
has reached my ears as well.

219
00:17:55,878 --> 00:17:59,075
Your sins against the people
of Degarashi Port are severe.

220
00:17:59,348 --> 00:18:03,648
Therefore, the Wagarashi Family
is to be dissolved as of today.

221
00:18:03,719 --> 00:18:04,811
Understood?

222
00:18:06,222 --> 00:18:08,087
Y-Yes, sire.

223
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:11,891
Today is an auspicious day.

224
00:18:12,161 --> 00:18:14,595
With this, the matter is settled.

225
00:18:21,971 --> 00:18:23,768
Thanks for the help, Naruto.

226
00:18:24,373 --> 00:18:26,671
Idate, this is good bye, huh?

227
00:18:28,611 --> 00:18:30,408
I've come to get the wounded.

228
00:18:31,414 --> 00:18:32,312
Ibiki.

229
00:18:32,815 --> 00:18:34,146
B-Big Brother!

230
00:18:35,184 --> 00:18:36,208
Where are the wounded?

231
00:18:36,919 --> 00:18:38,386
Over here.

232
00:18:39,188 --> 00:18:41,418
Okay, get him on the boat, quickly.

233
00:18:41,757 --> 00:18:43,054
R-Right.

234
00:18:45,361 --> 00:18:46,658
Um, excuse me.

235
00:18:46,929 --> 00:18:47,554
What is it?

236
00:18:49,498 --> 00:18:50,965
N-Nothing

237
00:18:54,804 --> 00:18:55,566
Brother!

238
00:18:56,706 --> 00:18:58,105
Wait, Big Brother!

239
00:19:00,676 --> 00:19:01,665
Who are you?

240
00:19:02,445 --> 00:19:06,472
The man who called me
Big Brother died three years ag

241
00:19:16,058 --> 00:19:20,051
<i>Big Brother... I figured out</i>
<i>the answer to the tenth problem!</i>

242
00:19:21,764 --> 00:19:24,130
<i>I'll never betray a comrade again!</i>

243
00:19:25,301 --> 00:19:27,462
<i>I can trust others now!</i>

244
00:19:36,012 --> 00:19:37,639
<i>He's looking good now.</i>

245
00:19:47,623 --> 00:19:49,853
'Bye, Idate. Let's meet again.

246
00:19:50,292 --> 00:19:51,782
Good bye. See you around.

247
00:19:52,428 --> 00:19:54,760
Yeah. You guys come again, too, okay?

248
00:19:55,698 --> 00:19:57,723
I wish you good health, Boss!

249
00:19:57,900 --> 00:19:58,696
Yeah...

250
00:20:00,569 --> 00:20:01,433
See ya!

251
00:20:02,171 --> 00:20:03,229
Take care!

252
00:20:06,175 --> 00:20:07,972
<i>An interesting guy as always.</i>

253
00:20:09,278 --> 00:20:12,247
<i>No wonder the Fifth Hokage</i>
<i>sees potential in him.</i>

254
00:20:13,449 --> 00:20:16,885
Naruto! Thanks!

255
00:20:17,353 --> 00:20:21,790
Idate! Next time,
it'll be a battle with me, believe it.

256
00:20:25,294 --> 00:20:26,955
Sasuke, does it hurt?

257
00:20:27,697 --> 00:20:28,186
No.

258
00:20:28,764 --> 00:20:29,822
Thank goodness.

259
00:20:30,066 --> 00:20:32,728
Those wounds will heal immediately
once we get back to the village.

260
00:20:34,003 --> 00:20:34,526
Right.

261
00:20:35,805 --> 00:20:37,796
